      in the 1970s, putting groups of songs on vinyl records was the most useful way of delivering music recordings. i would do it not because everyone else does it, but because it is so useful at that time. (which naturally is the reason everyone else would do it as well). if it was the 1890s, i might occasionally travel by horse....... etc
